snippet.title: Artist Life Simulator Teaser
snippet.description:
A Teaser for Artist Life Simulator, presenting some of the music,  background art assets and writings from the game. 
Currently last discount before exiting Early Access, 33% off at:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1643180/Artist_Life_Simulator/
